Выставка [The Mystery of Bansky "A genius mind"|https://banksy-zuerich.ch/]. Сзади описание:|This Card Is Blank Inside.|This Greetings Card is environmentally friendly.|The paper you are holding is from a sustainable source and the inks that we used are purely vegetable oil based. The pre-press (including plate making) is completely chemical free using no developers or fixers and leaves no waste liquids whatsoever. Any aluminium plates used are recycled. All offcuts and trimmings are pulped for newsprint and packaging (amongst other things). In short, virtually nothing is thrown away and anything we do dispose of is via a licensed waste agency.|We believe that our planet should be taken care of. However, we can't promise that we won't be hit by a massive comet soon, so live fast and party hard. We do. ©|As Banksy chooses to remain both anonymous and invisible, we have set up a little piggy bank for his royalty which if not claimed will be donated annually to a good cause. Banks does not produce or endorse greeting cards or print photo-canvases or paint commissions or sell freshly baked bagels.
Дошла до художественной галлереи [Kunsthaus|https://www.kunsthaus.ch/en/] в Цюрихе. Эта картина настроением напомнила Кулдигу, раннюю осень.
Теперь, когда я уехала, сестра продолжает эту серию городов Латвии.
